1. *Igrao* je fudbal na stadionu. (He played football at the stadium). 
2. On je *igrao* u njegovoj ekipi. (He played on his team).
3. *Igrajući*, on je postigao gol. (Playing, he scored a goal).
4. On će sutra *igrati* u njegovom timu. (He will play in his team tomorrow).
5. *Igrali* su dok je sunce svanulo. (They played until the sun rose).
6. *Igrala* je sa svojom sestrom. (She played with her sister).